OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCare homes: Extra fees for 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fappointments and garden    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Faccess criticised          
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Care home providers have been          
OL,6, criticised for charging top up fees to 
OL,7, residents for taking them to medical   
OL,8, appointments.                          
OL,10,FThe Older People's Commissioner Helena 
OL,11,FHerklots said providers should be open 
OL,12,Fand honest about extra fees and social 
OL,13,Fcare should be made free.              
OL,15,FSue Simms, whose dad is in a care home,
OL,16,Fsaid: "It feels mean and underhanded." 
OL,18,FThe Welsh government said care homes   
OL,19,Fwere legally required to set out any   
OL,20,Fextra charges.                         
